node.text: Yes I'm still in rainbow @opi nails 😂🙊. Listen you deserve a little pamper once in a while. Whenever I get moments to myself I always think pamper time is a waste of time and try do something 'productive'. Does anyone else feel like that?! I get a little skincare routine in every night but sometimes you need a little more. So I've started taking me moments during the week. Doing my nails with OPI nail strong or having a cuppa tea and biscuits or a cheeky facemask. Whatever it is. Do something where u show yourself some TLC 💛  also go check out OPI nature strong collection! Vegan cruelty free and made with naturally derived plant based ingredients 🥰 @opi @opi_professionals #OPINatureStrong #ad

node.text: We all change. Biologically we are changing every single second. Experiences in life, the people we meet, everything that comes through our senses changes us in some way. So don’t restrict people because you’re scared of change, don’t restrict yourself because of attachment to old thoughts or patterns that no longer fit your life. Allow yourself to grow evolve and expand!!!

Happy birthdayyyyyy @jayshetty YOU READY FOR SOME CHOCOLATE CAKE!? In the time I’ve known this beautiful man...It has become intensely clear to me that he is a seriously special human filled with SO much goodness. Theres so much I could say about you and who you are. You’re a man so aware, confident and comfortable with who he is. A man who is not afraid to be emotionally available to those he loves . a man who is so present with everyone he meets. A man who is so genuinely kind to the core of his heart that it’s almost hard to actually believe! A man who shares love unapologetically with no worries or fear about seeming too keen or too much. A man that finds deep joy in others success. a man that values and respects women SO deeply. A man who lives with sincere integrity and intention in everything he does. A man who carries no ego when it comes to apologizing no matter how small. A man who openly shares and embraces emotion. A man who works so incredibly hard to be better every single day. A man who takes every hardship in life as a true blessing. A man filled with wonder and big dreams. A man who has a beautiful vision and goal to uplift and empower people. 
I appreciate you so SO much. More and more every year. You join into silly dances with me, go on adventures with me to find little vegan restaurants around the world, tolerate my stubborn tendencies 😬 recognize the times when I need help vs encouraging me to help myself, let me DJ on car journeys and welcome my carpool karaoke screaming in your ear 😂😂 but more than anything the way I see u live and appreciate life, day in day out has made me a better person, you Always keep our spiritual growth the focus of our relationship and I really do feel so blessed you chose me to annoy you and grow learn and live life with! 💛
